    <p class="mb-4">
      Cyprus's Digital Nomad Visa offers an attractive package: year-round sunshine, English-speaking environment, up to 3 years of residence, and potentially significant tax benefits through non-dom status. The €3,500/month threshold is reasonable for the lifestyle on offer.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      The main limitations are lack of Schengen access (unlike Spain or Portugal) and island isolation. Cyprus is best suited for those who prioritize sunshine, English language, and tax efficiency over European travel mobility.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6">
      For British citizens post-Brexit seeking EU residence, Cyprus is particularly compelling—English-speaking, familiar culture, and straightforward immigration process. The 3-year potential makes it viable for medium-term planning.
    </p>

